{"id":234783,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/翻墙-配置-windows-7-上的原生纯-ipsec-vpn/","date":"2012-06-26T15:45:21Z","modified":"2012-06-26T15:45:21Z","title":"翻墙 | 配置 Windows 7 上的原生纯 IPSec VPN","content":"<p>原文：<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://igfw.net/archives/10259\">http://igfw.net/archives/10259</a></p>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<p>在Windows 7 系统上的原生地支持了纯 IPSec VPN，就是其“VPN类型”中的“IKEv2”。此类型VPN连接快、速度快、安全、稳定，本文主要学习的是IKEv2 VPN证书的安装方法（其实一般VPN服务商都会提供安装程序直接完成证书安装和VPN配置无需手动设置）。</p>\n<p>步骤略多，但实际很容易。先安装证书，然后创建VPN。</p>\n<div>\n<h3><strong><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://w3.owind.com/pub/binary/2012/06/26/install-ipsec-ikev2-vpn-on-windows-7/\">安装证书</a></strong></h3>\n<div>\n<p> </p>\n<p>先下载 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://owind.com/pca.crt\">http://owind.com/pca.crt</a>，可以先放到桌面。</p>\n<p>然后，开始菜单，打开 mmc 程序；</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s1.jpg\"><img title=\"s1\" src=\"http://w3.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"418\" height=\"514\" /></a></p>\n<p>选择 add/remove snap-in;</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s2.jpg\"><img title=\"s2\" src=\"http://w3.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" height=\"280\" /></a></p>\n<p>按图示添加证书管理</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s3.jpg\"><img title=\"s3\" src=\"http://w3.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"679\" height=\"474\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s4.jpg\"><img title=\"s4\" src=\"http://w3.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"675\" height=\"467\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s5.jpg\"><img title=\"s5\" src=\"http://w3.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"675\" height=\"478\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s6.jpg\"><img title=\"s6\" src=\"http://w3.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"677\" height=\"476\" /></a></p>\n<p>接着我们给系统添加VPN的CA证书；</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s7.jpg\"><img title=\"s7\" src=\"http://w3.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"662\" height=\"442\" /></a></p>\n<p>然后选择下载到本地的证书，导入。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s8.jpg\"><img title=\"s8\" src=\"http://w3.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"611\" height=\"486\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s9.jpg\"><img title=\"s9\" src=\"http://w3.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"657\" height=\"442\" /></a></p>\n<p>至此完成证书的添加。提醒：以后是我这的VPN就不用再次添加证书了。</p>\n</div>\n<h3><strong><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://w3.owind.com/pub/binary/2012/06/26/install-ipsec-ikev2-vpn-on-windows-7/\">手动创建VPN</a></strong></h3>\n<div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s10.jpg\"><img title=\"s10\" src=\"http://w3.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"328\" height=\"217\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s11.jpg\"><img title=\"s11\" src=\"http://w3.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"649\" height=\"390\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s12.jpg\"><img title=\"s12\" src=\"http://w3.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"616\" height=\"450\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s13.jpg\"><img title=\"s13\" src=\"http://w3.owind.com/pub/rsc/2012/06/s13.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"619\" height=\"454\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"n